&lt;div class="glossary-term" data-tag="city">
&lt;h2 id="adu-accessory-dwelling-unit">ADU (Accessory Dwelling Unit)&lt;a class="anchor" href="#adu-accessory-dwelling-unit">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
