&lt;h2 id="15-minute-city">15-Minute City&lt;a class="anchor" href="#15-minute-city">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>An urban planning concept where residents can reach daily necessities &amp;ndash; work, school, shopping, healthcare, parks &amp;ndash; within a 15-minute walk or bike ride. Popularized by Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo and professor Carlos Moreno.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Land Use &amp; Planning</title><link>https://seattle.urbanism-guide.com/pr-preview/59/glossary/land-use/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://seattle.urbanism-guide.com/pr-preview/59/glossary/land-use/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="land-use--planning-terms">Land Use &amp;amp; Planning Terms&lt;a class="anchor" href="#land-use--planning-terms">#&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
